OL,3,CNew tribute unveiled to 'Canary Girls'
OL,4,Cwho kept Britain's war machine going
OL,6,FReporter Zoe Muldoon was there to see
OL,7,Fthe unveiling of the new memorial in
OL,8,FChorley
OL,10,FA new memorial has been unveiled in
OL,11,FLancashire, honouring the women known
OL,12,Fas the 'Canary Girls'.
OL,14,FA special ceremony was held on
OL,15,FThursday to honour the women who were
OL,16,Fconscripted to work at Royal Ordnance
OL,17,FFactories, producing most of Britain's
OL,18,Fammunition during both world wars.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
