PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777036267
OL,3,CNew tribute unveiled to 'Canary Girls'
OL,4,Cwho kept Britain's war machine going
OL,6,FThe largest of those factories was in
OL,7,FChorley, where the permanent tribute
OL,8,Fis now housed.
OL,10,FThe vital role of the Canary Girls
OL,11,Fsupplying ammunition to the frontline
OL,12,Fis often overlooked, but their working
OL,13,Fconditions were often dangerous.
OL,15,FThe women were nicknamed the 'Canary
OL,16,FGirls' because their skin was stained
OL,17,Fyellow by toxic chemicals.
OL,19,FMany women were killed in explosions,
OL,20,Fothers left with permanent,
OL,21,Fdebilitating health problems.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
