CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777036267
OL,3,CNew tribute unveiled to 'Canary Girls'
OL,4,Cwho kept Britain's war machine going
OL,6,FOn Thursday, a tribute to the women
OL,7,Fwas unveiled at Buckshaw Village, just
OL,8,Fa stone's throw from what was the
OL,9,Flargest Royal Ordnance Factory.
OL,11,F"It's so that their story isn't
OL,12,Fforgotten", said Lindsey Barrow from
OL,13,FBuckshaw Village Women's Institute.
OL,15,F"Obviously at the time they weren't
OL,16,Fallowed to talk about where they
OL,17,Fworked and what they did - it was
OL,18,Fsecret. So these people couldn't share
OL,19,Ftheir stories and what we want to do
OL,20,Fis ensure that their legacy isn't
OL,21,Fforgotten."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
