PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777036267
OL,3,CNew tribute unveiled to 'Canary Girls'
OL,4,Cwho kept Britain's war machine going
OL,6,FThe mother of Parish Councillor Eric
OL,7,FJones was one of those called up to
OL,8,Fwork in the munitions factory in
OL,9,FEuxton.
OL,11,F"She made fuses with the deadly yellow
OL,12,Fpowder. She used to come home yellow,
OL,13,Fyour hair was yellow, everything was
OL,14,Fyellow. She didn't tell me much more
OL,15,Fbecause she was under the Official
OL,16,FSecrets Act."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
