PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777036267
OL,3,CNew tribute unveiled to 'Canary Girls'
OL,4,Cwho kept Britain's war machine going
OL,6,FThere's now a push for more
OL,7,Frecognition for these brave women,
OL,8,Fincluding a permanent tribute at the
OL,9,FNational Memorial Arboretum.
OL,11,FAnn Winstanley's mother was a Canary
OL,12,FGirl. She told ITV News "They never
OL,13,Freally had any real acknowledgement of
OL,14,Ftheir work.
OL,16,F"It was sad really, she said (to me)
OL,17,Feverybody else seemed to get
OL,18,Fsomething. She said, your dad got his
OL,19,Fmedals, the school children got a
OL,20,Fletter off the King, and we got
OL,21,Fnothing.
OL,26,@xD@^pmxD@dpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
